## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project is a simple machine learning implementation to classify breast cancer tumors as **Malignant (M)** or **Benign (B)**.

The goal of this project was to practice:

* Data preprocessing
* Model training
* Hyperparameter tuning
* Model comparison

---

## ğŸ“‚ Dataset

* Dataset downloaded using **Kaggle API**
* Dataset: Breast Cancer Wisconsin Dataset
* Downloaded directly into local environment using Kaggle API
* Stored and processed locally

